238
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:45,050
It's incredibly cheap.

239
00:13:45,100 --> 00:13:47,930
Now, a few years ago, we improved
police cars, and last week,

240
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:50,170
~ we improved ambulances.
